<subSubSection pageId="44" pageNumber="45" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="44.[189,1399,1574,1742]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
In describing this genus, which was based on two species from 
<collectingCountry box="[910,1026,1574,1600]" name="Sri Lanka" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Sri Lanka</collectingCountry>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Johnson C." box="[1035,1216,1574,1600]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="257 - 275" refId="ref16850" refString="Johnson C. 1988. Revision of Sri Lankan Acrotrichines (Coleoptera: Ptiliidae). Revue Suisse de Zoologie 95: 257 - 275. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 79651" type="journal article" year="1988">Johnson (1988)</bibRefCitation>
noted that there were no features distinguishing it from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Motschulsky" authorityYear="1848" box="[644,775,1609,1635]" class="Insecta" family="Ptiliidae" genus="Acrotrichis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[644,775,1609,1635]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Acrotrichis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
except for the approximate metacoxae separated only by a narrow bifurcate extension of the metaventrum. Future research on the subgenera of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Motschulsky" authorityYear="1848" box="[1228,1359,1644,1670]" class="Insecta" family="Ptiliidae" genus="Acrotrichis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1228,1359,1644,1670]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Acrotrichis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(in progress) may reduce the status of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Johnson" authorityYear="1988" box="[599,731,1680,1706]" class="Insecta" family="Ptiliidae" genus="Storicricha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[599,731,1680,1706]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Storicricha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to that level. Four additional species have been added to the genus recently from 
<collectingCountry box="[474,528,1715,1741]" name="Peru" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Peru</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Darby M." box="[543,704,1715,1742]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="179 - 203" refId="ref16490" refString="Darby M. 2017 b. Studies of Peruvian Ptiliidae (Coleoptera) 6: new species and records of Acrotrichini. Entomologist's Monthly Magazine 153: 179 - 203." type="journal article" year="2017">Darby 2017b</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
